### Crear nova pala
POST http://localhost:5000/api/palas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id_pala": "PALA001",
  "nombre": "Bullpadel Vertex 03",
  "peso": 365,
  "stock": 12,
  "imagenes": ["https://example.com/vertex1.jpg", "https://example.com/vertex2.jpg"],
  "marca": "Bullpadel",
  "precio": 199.99,
  "descripcion": "Pala de potència amb bon control.",
  "tipo": "potencia"
}

### Obtenir totes les pales
GET http://localhost:5000/api/palas HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Obtenir una pala per ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/palas/6909bcd32c9ed34f6b5cdf58 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

### Actualitzar pala
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/palas/6909bcd32c9ed34f6b5cdf58 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "stock": 10,
  "precio": 189.99
}

### Eliminar pala
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/palas/6909bcd32c9ed34f6b5cdf58 HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json
